Question: Both classic cars are facing the same direction.

Reference Answer: False

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the classic car facing the same direction as the other?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the classic car facing the same direction as the other?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER1}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
